  "notes": [
    "If you have some chorizo, feel free to use it instead of bacon. Same with any vegetables you have left in the fridge."
  ],
  "overnight": false,
  "slug": "frittata-with-vegetables",
  "steps": [
    {
      "name": "",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "Whisk the eggs together with milk or yogurt, and salt, and leave for at least 15 minutes.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Cut bacon into 1/2 cm cubes.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Heat a large skillet on medium-high heat, and fry bacon until crispy.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Prepare the vegetables. **Onion:** peel, halve, and cut into medium dice. **Garlic:** peel, and cut into small pieces. **Chili:** remove the seeds, and thinly slice. **Green beans:** remove the ends, and cut into 5 cm pieces. **Zucchini:** cut into thin half-moons. **Bell peppers:** remove the seeds, and cut into 1/2 thin strips.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the onions, garlic, and chili to the skillet, reduce the heat to medium, and cook until they start to crisp.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add hard vegetables to the skillet — green beans, and cook for several minutes.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the rest of the vegetables to the skillet, salt, and cook, stirring occasionally, until soft and slightly browned.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Remove everything from the skillet.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Reduce the heat to low, and melt 1 tbsp of butter (less or none if there is still a lot of fat in the pan).",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Quickly rewhisk the eggs, and pour them onto the skillet.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Distribute the vegetables on top of the eggs.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Cook covered until the eggs are firm.",
          "pause": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
